{"tid":403622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"５０００人集會反港獨　促革走戴耀廷　嚴懲中大生","createTime":"2017-09-17T10:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T14:38:24.000Z","uid":141461,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6425caaa6981b0b33989862d569be95243d7b40","tid":403622,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/183935_bd33ecf49496f1362e829160c566c8c7.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F183935_bd33ecf49496f1362e829160c566c8c7.JPG&h=e4fced3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯及多個團體下午在添馬公園發起「反港獨、反冷血、反偽學吶喊大會」，關注大學近日出現港獨言論，以及要求港大革走佔領行動發起人戴耀廷的教職；大會指有5000人參與。集會期間，一名女子不適暈倒，即場接受急救。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯表示，戴耀廷提出違法佔領後，引起一系列不安寧及暴動事件，而近日大學出現冷血的言論，有違教育精神，罪魁禍首是戴耀廷，斥戴挑戰法律精神，提出違法達義，質疑是教人犯法，導致社會大亂，戴搞佔領導致港獨思潮出現，而佔中距今數年，須撥亂反正，革走戴耀廷。對於戴的案件即將審理，何否認向法庭施壓。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員周浩鼎表示，近日大學出現主張港獨的言論，是禮崩樂壞，斥有人以言論自由作擋箭牌，為壞行開脫，希望社會出聲駁斥歪理，以免為禍下一代。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員邵家輝指，港獨違憲違法，近期少撮人在大學不斷宣揚港獨，港人不能再沉默，要表態不支持此事。對於有聲音指校外做的事與校內教職無關，邵家輝反問「唔通何君堯議員喺出面殺人放火，唔喺立法會嘅話，就唔需要受懲罰咩？」他認為自由要有底線。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員陳恒鑌表示，自己早前就教大出現港獨標語的事，發起網上聯署，3天就收到約3000個簽名，被問到是否干預學校內政，他認為，這是每個人都應出聲的事，有不對的事就要站出來講，否則就會「集非成是」，而香港多年來亦非「教育歸教育，政治歸政治」，現時部分較激進的人都是在大學教書。"},{"pid":"00fbcdef5fe19ea278d5468dbf9d53ccbd1b71fa","tid":403622,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:42:44.000Z","msg":"5000人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3211da383bd99740e49364c03dc626cb8f1c326","tid":403622,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"唔係有8萬人簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ebc2cfb05ffb33e9f3e3ec0d19e570352a101a","tid":403622,"uid":2054,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:42:58.000Z","msg":"700萬 - 5000人支持戴耀廷 同 中大學生"},{"pid":"fa1d623b1da832d8f74fa1ef98473f6fc1275e1d","tid":403622,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2002dcaa5ec54131b0e671e3f338eff8be60a30f","tid":403622,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"乜係偽學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73b68cf288e31a2ad069f6a434a7daf606f8d94","tid":403622,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ede2fcbc796a5b0748ffd86877b50bcd509db3","tid":403622,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:12:38.000Z","msg":"戴妖當日唔一幹到底<br />\n<br />\n一味半桶水、釋出善意、篤友出賣友軍, <br />\n<br />\n全面失敗後, 依家咪比人反咬<br />\n<br />\n所以故事教訓: <br />\n一係唔做, 一做就要徹底, 一幹到底<br />\n不達目的誓不罷休"},{"pid":"1ebec04318c00a01dbfd716d2b22a9ae3a1c193e","tid":403622,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:30:44.000Z","msg":"得5000，咁渣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024018cbc8916d4fc5dc28aad7737849c57082c1","tid":403622,"uid":16731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:32:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d9f59a215f56e6bb6ffb9fe76c1652d3eb6ad80","tid":403622,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:34:21.000Z","msg":"咁即係仲有冇出席既7百幾萬香港人都支持港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01670b74e28595d0957b813bf33cec3c1635c65","tid":403622,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:49:47.000Z","msg":"文革式批鬥開始？"},{"pid":"3f6d17b0b53b9c6c8899817705120c55058cd88d","tid":403622,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c74121d132a47c494174696e041c64cebc774f7","tid":403622,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁即係仲有冇出席既7百幾萬香港人都支持港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼有738萬人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29518504d800928bf2416edf3ba858b137ddbd6e","tid":403622,"uid":97299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:12:30.000Z","msg":"集非成是？<br />\n賊喊捉賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838424c5a379e6f67b1e0594ca382a559b11d31c","tid":403622,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:14:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戴妖當日唔一幹到底<br />\n<br />\n一味半桶水、釋出善意、篤友出賣友軍, <br />\n<br />\n全面失敗後, 依家咪比人反咬<br />\n<br />\n所以故事教訓: <br />\n一係唔做, 一做就要徹底, 一幹到底<br />\n不達目的誓不罷休</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條撚屌根本一開始就冇諗住要贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三子一路都係想比人拉之後坐監<br />\n點知依家差唔多個個都有得坐，佢3個自首都冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6296b132bf07873880f1a1d5b6f649ab44fc02b2","tid":403622,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:15:15.000Z","msg":"乱字都唔識寫仲好意思話自己愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df1b4f50058dc82db6c42b8e31362dd7ac8e149","tid":403622,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:23:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e13dff816427dde2ef6d1f2155fb9377588c6afb","tid":403622,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"又係廢老, 廢中, 大媽"}]}